de.ovgu.featureide.cloneanalysis.results

Class CPDResultConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.cloneanalysis.results.CPDResultConverter

  • public class CPDResultConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    CPD is optimized for speed and badly documented, which sadly results in badly formatted results. This class handles the conversion of CPDs results into a better format.
    Author:
    Konstantin Tonscheidt
    See Also:
    CloneAnalysisResults, Clone

      • checkForIntervariance

        public static boolean checkForIntervariance(java.util.Set<CloneOccurence> occurences)
        Checks the clones occurences. If occurences exist in different projects or, in the case of FeatureProjects, in different feature folders, the clone is intervariant.
        Parameters:
        occurences - the complete Set of the clones occurences.
        Returns:
        true if the clone is intervariant, false else.
